<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - Dress Barn upgraded.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - Dress Barn upgraded.</headline>
<dateline>SAN FRANCISCO 1997-05-23</dateline>
<text>
<p>Robertson, Stephens &amp; Co said it upgraded its rating on Dress Barn Inc to a buy from market performer.</p>
<p>-- cited Dress Barn's merchandise strategy as a significant factor in improved sales and gross margin trends.</p>
